","author":"adonai","authorid":"155630","dateline":"2018-12-6 23:16","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41854252&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">凛凛233 发表于 2018-12-6 20:27</font></a><br />\r\n写的真好<br />\r\n不过吧，霙会嫉妒希美吗</div><br />\n可能到不了嫉妒的程度，我觉得更多的是羡慕、钦佩和欣赏，我感觉不到霙这方面的负面情绪，感觉就是一个从没有过坏心思的天使","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"897","username":"adonai","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"896","dbdateline":"1544109375","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41856026","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"糖尔","authorid":"449490","dateline":"2018-12-6 23:21","message":"太能感同身受了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/140.png\" /><br />\n从小学有个很憧憬的朋友，高考后她去了top5我却在个垃圾大学念书，联系从两天一次减到现在几个月一次，虽然真的聊起来还是很亲密但是现在每次想要联系对方总是害怕打扰到她，总是担心她有了比我更重要的朋友，我明白她在离我越来越远，想要去触碰却又收回手的感觉<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/140.png\" /><br />\n这片无论是百合还是非百合角度都很打动人，呜哇<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/139.png\" /><img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/139.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"898","username":"糖尔","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"897","dbdateline":"1544109709","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41856030","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"zuesphilip","authorid":"474016","dateline":"2018-12-6 23:22","message":"我暂时已经看不进其他任何动画了，这种戒断反应真是久违几年了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/002.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/fi/app/saraba1st/id1221237470?mt=8\"><font color=\"#999999\">-- 来自 能看大图的 Stage1官方 iOS客户端</font></a>","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"899","username":"zuesphilip","adminid":"0","groupid":"29","memberstatus":"0","number":"898","dbdateline":"1544109759","groupiconid":"5"},{"pid":"418